Fine-Tune Permissions for SFTP Users

Improve security by granting your SFTP users different levels of access. At the user level, assign access to view, edit, download from, and upload to top-level SFTP folders. You can also apply an additional layer of access by customizing each userâ€™s home directory.

Where: This change applies to all Marketing Cloud Engagement editions.

When: This feature is available on a rolling basis starting in May 2024.
title: Fine-Tune Permissions for SFTP Users in Salesforce
